channel.description: Hey, I really need a Coal miner for the SW of Draynor. And I need it to bank. I have posted this on 4 sites I think and I haven't had any help so far... Please would you be able to help me? I am starting to learn SCAR but I'm a complete loser and give up easily sometimes, and with programming that's one of those times. Many thanks in advance. And I haven't seen any SCAR script like this, so if you did do it, you'd be(To the best of my knowledge) the first... wouldn't you wanna be the first to do something? ;) Other than posting on this topic?:) Many thanks in advance.
